THERE AIN'T NOTHING SPECIAL
ABOUT YOU, BUT IF YOU WERE

26:43.635 --> 26:55.580
SAVED, YOU GOT TO SHOW THAT YOU
WERE WORTHY OF IT.
AND THAT HAS BEEN THE DRIVING
FORCE IN MY LIFE.

26:55.647 --> 27:03.555
>> Wertheim: AS A WAY TO HONOR
YOUR FAMILY THAT PERISHED.
>> Stern: YEAH.
>> Wertheim: AFTER THE GERMAN

27:03.621 --> 27:11.162
ARMY'S SURRENDER, GUY STERN AND
THE OTHER RITCHIE BOYS TOOK ON A
NEW ASSIGNMENT: HUNTING DOWN TOP
NAZI OFFICERS RESPONSIBLE FOR

27:11.229 --> 27:16.101
THE ATROCITIES THAT KILLED SO
MANY, INCLUDING MANY OF THEIR
LOVED ONES.
WHEN WE COME BACK, WE'LL HEAR

27:16.167 --> 27:23.608
ABOUT SOME OF THE SURPRISING
WAYS GUY STERN AND THE OTHER
RITCHIE BOYS WERE ABLE TO
IDENTIFY SUSPECTED NAZI WAR

27:23.675 --> 27:34.552
CRIMINALS, MANY OF WHOM LATER
