CONTINUOUS FLOW OF RELIABLE
INFORMATION THAT REALLY HELPED

28:23.968 --> 28:31.910
EXPEDITE THE END OF THE WAR.
>> Wertheim: THIS HAD A REAL
MATERIAL IMPACT ON WORLD WAR II.
>> Stern: YES

28:31.976 --> 28:39.984
>> Wertheim: FOR 99-YEAR-OLD GUY
STERN, A GERMAN JEW WHOSE ENTIRE
FAMILY WAS KILLED BY THE NAZIS,
THE ALLIES' VICTORY OVER HITLER

