SURRENDER, THE RITCHIE BOYS TOOK

29:21.993 --> 29:27.999
ON THE DIFFICULT TASK OF
IDENTIFYING AND TRACKING DOWN
NAZI CRIMINALS.
LONGTIME YALE AND PRINCETON

29:28.066 --> 29:38.176
PROFESSOR VICTOR BROMBERT HELPED
ENACT THE OFFICIAL ALLIED POLICY
OF REMOVING NAZI INFLUENCE FROM
GERMAN PUBLIC LIFE, KNOWN AS DE-

29:38.243 --> 29:46.851
NAZIFICATION.
