SURRENDERS, AND YOU'RE ASSIGNED
TO THE DE-NAZIFICATION PROCESS.

29:46.918 --> 29:55.994
WHAT- WHAT DID THAT ENTAIL?
>> Brombert: WE WERE SUPPOSED TO
ARREST IMPORTANT NAZI OFFICIALS,
NOT JUST ANY NAZI PARTY MEMBER.

29:56.060 --> 30:05.970
IT WAS VERY, VERY HARD, VERY
DIFFICULT AND VERY RARE TO HAVE
A GERMAN DENOUNCE ANOTHER GERMAN
AT THAT POINT.

30:06.037 --> 30:15.246
NOW IS IT BECAUSE THEY WERE
AFRAID THAT THE NAZIS MIGHT COME
BACK, THAT IT'S NOT OVER?
OR IS IT JUST A HABIT OR HABIT

30:15.313 --> 30:22.420
OF OBEDIENCE OR DIGNITY?
