AND AT GREAT EFFORT WE FOUND
PEOPLE, WE ARRESTED THEM, WE

30:22.487 --> 30:28.493
WERE PROUD OF DOING THAT.
>> Wertheim: AS PART OF DE-
NAZIFICATION, PHOTOS OF NAZI
ATROCITIES WERE POSTED IN GERMAN

