SHOP WINDOWS AND RITCHIE BOYS
LED THE COUNTRY'S CITIZENS ON
TOURS OF THE CONCENTRATION CAMPS
TO EDUCATE THE LOCAL POPULATION

30:38.002 --> 30:43.975
ABOUT THE EVIL HITLER HAD
PERPETRATED.
SOMETIMES ENTIRE GERMAN TOWNS
WERE FORCED TO PAY RESPECTS TO

30:44.042 --> 30:51.382
THE DEAD.
