INTERVIEW GERMAN CIVILIANS TO
HELP GAUGE THE DEGREE TO WHICH

30:51.449 --> 30:58.022
THEY HAD SERVED THE NAZI CAUSE
AND DETERMINE WHICH ONES SHOULD
BE PUNISHED.
